<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CrossFit Atlas</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: light;
        --bg: #f3eee5;
        --panel: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);
        --ink: #1b1b1b;
        --muted: #64584a;
        --accent: #cf4420;
        --accent-dark: #8e2007;
        --line: rgba(27, 27, 27, 0.12);
      }
      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: "Trebuchet MS", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        color: var(--ink);
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(207, 68, 32, 0.15), transparent 35%),
          radial-gradient(circle at right, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08), transparent 20%),
          linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f3ec 0%, #efe4d1 48%, #e3d8c6 100%);
      }
      .shell {
        max-width: 1180px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 32px 20px 60px;
      }
      .hero {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
        gap: 28px;
        align-items: stretch;
      }
      .card {
        background: var(--panel);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 28px;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(56, 32, 12, 0.12);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      }
      .headline {
        padding: 40px;
      }
      .eyebrow {
        display: inline-flex;
        padding: 8px 12px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-size: 0.72rem;
        background: rgba(207, 68, 32, 0.12);
        color: var(--accent-dark);
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 5vw, 4.9rem);
        line-height: 0.92;
        margin: 18px 0 18px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }
      p {
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: var(--muted);
      }
      .stats {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 14px;
        margin-top: 24px;
      }
      .stat {
        padding: 18px;
        border-radius: 18px;
        background: rgba(27, 27, 27, 0.04);
      }
      .stat strong {
        display: block;
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
        color: var(--ink);
      }
      .features {
        margin-top: 28px;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 18px;
      }
      .feature {
        padding: 22px;
        border-radius: 22px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
        border: 1px solid rgba(27, 27, 27, 0.08);
      }
      .feature h2 {
        margin: 0 0 10px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      }
      .form-card {
        padding: 28px;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .form-card::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: auto -40px -70px auto;
        width: 180px;
        height: 180px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(207, 68, 32, 0.32), transparent 70%);
      }
      form {
        display: grid;
        gap: 14px;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
      }
      label {
        display: grid;
        gap: 8px;
        font-size: 0.92rem;
        color: var(--muted);
      }
      input, textarea, button {
        width: 100%;
        border-radius: 16px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(27, 27, 27, 0.14);
        padding: 14px 16px;
        font: inherit;
      }
      input, textarea {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
      }
      textarea {
        min-height: 130px;
        resize: vertical;
      }
      button {
        cursor: pointer;
        border: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent) 0%, var(--accent-dark) 100%);
        color: white;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }
      .error {
        border-radius: 14px;
        padding: 12px 14px;
        background: rgba(143, 16, 16, 0.08);
        color: #7a1717;
      }
      @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .hero {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
        .stats,
        .features {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="shell">
      <section class="hero">
        <article class="card headline">
          <span class="eyebrow">CrossFit Atlas</span>
          <h1>Fuerza real. Técnica limpia. Comunidad fuerte.</h1>
          <p>
            Entrenamiento funcional guiado por coaches certificados, grupos reducidos y una
            cultura de progreso medible. Atlas combina intensidad, movilidad y seguimiento
            personalizado para atletas nuevos y avanzados.
          </p>

          <div class="stats">
            <div class="stat">
              <strong>06:00</strong>
              Primer turno del día
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <strong>12</strong>
              Personas por clase
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <strong>7 días</strong>
              De programación semanal
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="features">
            <div class="feature">
              <h2>On Ramp</h2>
              <p>Programa inicial de 4 sesiones para técnica, movilidad y adaptación progresiva.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
              <h2>Open Gym</h2>
              <p>Franjas libres para practicar levantamientos, accesorios y skill work.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
              <h2>Recovery</h2>
              <p>Bloques guiados de respiración, descarga y movilidad para sostener la carga semanal.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <aside class="card form-card">
          <h2>Solicita información</h2>
          <p>Déjanos tus datos y te contactamos con planes, horarios y clase de prueba.</p>

          <% if (error) { %>
            <div class="error"><%= error %></div>
          <% } %>

          <form action="/contact" method="post">
            <label>
              Nombre completo
              <input type="text" name="full_name" value="<%= form.full_name %>" required>
            </label>
            <label>
              Email
              <input type="email" name="email" value="<%= form.email %>" required>
            </label>
            <label>
              Teléfono
              <input type="text" name="phone" value="<%= form.phone %>">
            </label>
            <label>
              Mensaje
              <textarea name="message" required><%= form.message %></textarea>
            </label>
            <button type="submit">Enviar consulta</button>
          </form>
        </aside>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

